= Familiarization Mock Overview

#info-box[
  *Purpose:*
  - Introduce students to all GMAT question formats
  - Reduce test anxiety by removing unfamiliarity
  - NOT used for cycle placement (no score recorded)
  - Prepare students for the actual Placement Assessment
]

#warning-box[
  *Important:* This is an educational introduction, not an evaluation. Encourage students to:
  - Take their time to understand each question type
  - Ask questions about formats or instructions
  - Focus on learning the mechanics, not achieving a score
]

